{"data":[{"date":"13:37 08/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/u19-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Indonesia trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i qua 7/7.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/7, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Indonesia. D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-1 \u1edf ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u00e1i Lan khi\u1ebfn nguy c\u01a1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hoang Anh Tuan\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/u19-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;V\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y xem nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, b\u1edfi Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mong \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i t\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng U19 Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 fair-play \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U19 Singapore. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u00f4ng Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp hay kh\u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n l\u1eabn kh\u00e1t v\u1ecdng&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n d\u00e0i ng\u00e0y \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 18/10 t\u1edbi 4/11/2018.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00dac v\u00e0 Jordan. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190633.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190633.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-1 U19 Indonesia (Gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1eb9p \u0111i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y sau khi ch\u00fang ta thua U19 Indonesia, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n v\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-ngay-hom-nay-372-190607.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-ngay-hom-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-ngay-hom-nay-372-190607.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-1 U19 Indonesia (KT): T\u00ednh to\u00e1n sai l\u1ea7m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i sau khi ch\u00fang ta thua U19 Indonesia, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n v\u00e0o...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4055","checkdouble":"190686"},{"date":"14:08 08/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TPHCM 19h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/nhan-dinh-ha-noi-vs-tphcm-19h00-ngay-87-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TPHCM l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7 (V\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TPHCM 19h00 ng\u00e0y 87 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TPHCM 19h00 ng\u00e0y 87 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/nhan-dinh-ha-noi-vs-tp-hcm-vong-18-v-league-2018-3-rs650.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TPHCM</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TPHCM: 4-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 2-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League 201, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i\u00a0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi chu\u1ed7i 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Th\u1ebf l\u00e0, sau 17 v\u00f2ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam v\u1eabn v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 44 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u01a1n t\u1edbi 15 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, TPHCM \u0111ang n\u1eb1m b\u1eb9p d\u00ed \u1edf \u0111\u00e1y BXH v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 15 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 12 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Sau 17 tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 16 b\u00e0n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 6 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u1edf 8 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Toshiya Mira v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 7/8 tr\u1eadn, ghi t\u1edbi 26 b\u00e0n (trung b\u00ecnh h\u01a1n 3 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn). T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2\u00e0 4-0, h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 4-1 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, TPHCM t\u1eebng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-4 ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i V-League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 4 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf V-League.<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 5 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: V\u0103n C\u00f4ng \u2013 V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, Oloya, V\u0103n Th\u00e0nh, Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n+ H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh: Thanh Di\u1ec7p \u2013 V\u0103n Ho\u00e0n, \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n Robert, \u0110\u00ecnh B\u1ea3o, V\u0103n Thu\u1eadn, H\u1eefu Tu\u1ea5n, C\u00f4ng Hi\u1ec3n, Paulo Tavares, Phi S\u01a1n, Quang Nam, H\u1ea3i Anh.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4054","checkdouble":"190690"},{"date":"14:20 08/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (H1): R\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/truc-tiep-quang-nam-vs-binh-duong-17h00-ngay-87-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20p