n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4051","checkdouble":"190695"},{"date":"14:42 08/07","title":"C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real v\u1ec1 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ramon Calderon cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real khi n\u1ea3y sinh \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Calderon c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span> \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng`\u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh 5 danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 34 v\u00e0o n\u0103m sau. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V v\u1eabn tin r\u1eb1ng CR7 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0a Real t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 c\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Calderon \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch cho r\u1eb1ng Real kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u00e1n Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch cho r\u1eb1ng Real kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u00e1n Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Calderon cho r\u1eb1ng Real kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u00e1n Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cN\u1ebfu Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tham gia t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a trong v\u00f2ng 9 n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFlorentino Perez \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Real qua c\u00e1c n\u0103m. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebf th\u1eeba t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng t\u1eebng x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Iker Casillas v\u00e0 Raul.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng Perez kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 anh cao nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn. Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho th\u1ea5y Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Neymar g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Calderon \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ronaldo ch\u1ecdn Juve</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo c\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Juventus l\u1eabn Serie A \u0111ang mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJuventus t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1eady n\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u1ea1 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn Bianconeri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Juventus c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Serie A. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Champions League. Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t cho l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. V\u1eady n\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u CLB \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/messi-va-ronaldo-xuat-hien-tren-khan-dai-trong-tran-nga-vs-croatia-465-190659.html\">Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-cap-doi-khien-messi-va-ronaldo-cung-phai-ghen-ti-421-190615.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ghen t\u1ecb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4050","checkdouble":"190689"},{"date":"16:22 08/07","title":"Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/8/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00f3ng thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec1u x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Juventus \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 CR7.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3m quan c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric cho r\u1eb1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nghi\u0303 anh \u00e2\u0301y se\u0303 r\u01a1\u0300i Real Madrid. Ronaldo la\u0300 c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 xu\u00e2\u0301t s\u0103\u0301c nh\u00e2\u0301t th\u00ea\u0301 gi\u01a1\u0301i, t\u00f4i mu\u00f4\u0301n anh \u00e2\u0301y \u01a1\u0309 la\u0323i vi\u0300 \u0111i\u00ea\u0300u na\u0300y co\u0301 y\u0301 nghi\u0303a r\u00e2\u0301t quan tro\u0323ng v\u1edbi CLB.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ha\u0303y ch\u01a1\u0300 xem \u0111i\u00ea\u0300u gi\u0300 se\u0303 xa\u0309y ra. Se\u0303 th\u00e2\u0323t tuy\u00ea\u0323t v\u01a1\u0300i n\u00ea\u0301u Ronaldo ti\u00ea\u0301p tu\u0323c g\u0103\u0301n bo\u0301 v\u01a1\u0301i Real Madrid. T\u00f4i ch\u0103\u0309ng th\u00ea\u0309 t\u01b0\u01a1\u0323ng t\u01b0\u01a1\u0323ng n\u00f4\u0309i hi\u0300nh a\u0309nh anh \u00e2\u0301y khoa\u0301c a\u0301o \u0111\u00f4\u0323i bo\u0301ng kha\u0301c\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Du\u0300 tin \u0111\u00f4\u0300n Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhan nh\u1ea3n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ca\u0309 Juventus l\u00e2\u0303n Real Madrid \u0111\u00ea\u0300u ch\u01b0a co\u0301 \u0111\u00f4\u0323ng tha\u0301i chi\u0301nh th\u01b0\u0301c na\u0300o v\u00ea\u0300 vi\u00ea\u0323c n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e2\u0323m chi\u0301, c\u01b0\u0323u CEO AC Milan, Adriano Galliani m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng cho bi\u00ea\u0301t \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a h\u00ea\u0300 nghe b\u00e2\u0301t c\u01b0\u0301 th\u00f4ng tin na\u0300o v\u00ea\u0300 th\u01b0\u01a1ng vu\u0323 Cristiano Ronaldo du\u0300 m\u00ecnh la\u0300 ba\u0323n th\u00e2n cu\u0309a Florentino Perez.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo-180-190689.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo-180-190689.html\">C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real v\u1ec1 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ramon Calderon cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real khi n\u1ea3y sinh \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bao-than-real-xat-muoi-vao-vet-thuong-long-cua-neymar-sau-tran-thua-bi-421-190600.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/bao-than-real-xat-muoi-vao-vet-thuong-long-cua-neymar-sau-tran-thua-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bao-than-real-xat-muoi-vao-vet-thuong-long-cua-neymar-sau-tran-thua-bi-421-190600.html\">B\u00e1o th\u00e2n Real x\u00e1t mu\u1ed1i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Neymar sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Neymar, \u00f4ng Tomas Roncero -T\u1ed5ng bi\u00ean t\u1eadp t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u00e2n Real, AS kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao Brazil c\u00f2n l\u00e2u m\u1edbi s\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-sao-khung-real-madrid-180-190592.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/2/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-sao-khung-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-sao-khung-real-madrid-180-190592.html\">Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nJuventus mua Marcelo, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4049","checkdouble":"190697"},{"date":"12:28 08/07","title":"Klopp m\u1eebng r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a 2 t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/klopp-mung-ro-voi-man-trinh-dien-cua-2-tan-binh-bom-tan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Jurgen Klopp ca ng\u1ee3i Fabinho v\u00e0 Keita \u2013 2 t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8.\r\n</h2><h2>Liverpool v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o 2 bom t\u1ea5n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Chester v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 7-0, v\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 45 ph\u00fat. Klopp n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Naby Keita &ndash; t\u00e2n binh 48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, trong khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabinho c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Klopp cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 cho h\u1ecd. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef chung v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng trong tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u1ed5n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Fabinho s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi, trong khi Naby c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2-3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa, khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp ca ng\u1ee3i Fabinho v\u00e0 Keita\" title=\"Fabinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/fabinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jurgen Klopp ca ng\u1ee3i Fabinho v\u00e0 Keita</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Naby \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Leipzig, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u00e9n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t, suy ngh\u0129 nhanh v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, pressing, nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, AS Monaco ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Fabinho c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa. D\u00f9 sao, kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Klopp ca ng\u1ee3i Fabinho v\u00e0 Keita.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0, t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 n\u00e0y. Klopp vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Trent Alexander-Arnold h\u1ebft l\u1eddi.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam-172-190673.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/28/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam-172-190673.html\">Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m</span><br>\r\nSadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish-172-190672.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish-172-190672.html\">Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u0103n sao tr\u1ebb h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nLiverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. H\u1ecd quy\u1ebft s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4048","checkdouble":"190681"},{"date":"16:48 08/07","title":"MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 Anthony Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/24/mu-quyet-tam-lam-kho-anthony-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Anthony Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU, nh\u01b0ng BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Martial kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U. Theo \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Anthony Martial r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Anthony Martial r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/mu-quyet-tam-lam-kho-anthony-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 23 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Old Trafford, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Martial ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, sau Sanchez v\u00e0 Rashford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-san-sang-trao-doi-cau-thu-voi-mu-172-186792.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Martial</span>, PSG, Juventus v\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Martial ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anthony Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU, nh\u01b0ng BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial se dut ao chia tay MU he nay\" title=\"Martial s\u1ebd d\u1ee9t \u00e1o chia tay MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Martial \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, M.U \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Martial \u1edf l\u1ea1i, Mourinho h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u1edbi Lukaku.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMartial hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bayern Munich l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh, M.U s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4047","checkdouble":"190682"},{"date":"09:33 08/07","title":"Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fekir","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lyon, Jean-Michel Aulas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Fekir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nabil Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lyon. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi t\u1edbi 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ligue 1, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNabil Fekir r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 trung phong c\u1eafm. HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Fekir, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Liverpool th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Martial, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lyon kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Fekir cho Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lyon, Jean-Michel Aulas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nabil Fekir\" title=\"Nabil Fekir\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/liverpool-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-tuyen-phap-len-60-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Fekir s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Lyon, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Fekir h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Lyon, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cFekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4046","checkdouble":"190670"},{"date":"09:55 08/07","title":"\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/everton-va-tottenham-muon-mua-mina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Colombia.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mina t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean \u0110T Colombia, Yerry Mina \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Anh h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Davinson Sanchez th\u00e0nh c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 22 v\u00e0 23 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Colombia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi ri\u00eang Mina, anh c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Colombia. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai trong \u0111\u1ed9i. Khi b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cao 1m95 c\u1ee7a Mina l\u00e0 v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Colombia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Tottenham-va-Everton-muon-mua-Yerry-Mina-cua-Barcelona-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Colombia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Mina m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Colombia tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Mina l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, gi\u00fap Los Cafeteros \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. D\u00f9 Colombia sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nYerry Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca t\u1eadu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Palmeiras \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018. Nh\u01b0ng sau m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2017/18, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y anh. Mina t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Hang-thai-Barca-hut-khach-Premier-League-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, Barca t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea9y Mina ngay trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c g\u00ec khi trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u201chot\u201d tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, t\u1edd The Sun ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina. Tottenham c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft Davinson Sanchez v\u00e0 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Mina h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Everton l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i Barca l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Mina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Samuel Umtiti v\u00e0 Gerard Pique. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 4 \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Blaugrana mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-4-muc-tieu-sieu-khung-duoc-barca-nham-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-190595.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 4 M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca nh\u1eafm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-gui-loi-de-nghi-thu-2-mua-sao-chelsea-180-190491.html\">Barca g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 mua sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/messi-muon-barca-mua-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu-172-190483.html\">Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-tiep-tuc-nhan-don-dau-tren-ttcn-180-190407.html\">Barca ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au tr\u00ean TTCN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/willian-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-duoc-barca-quan-tam-421-190386.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quan t\u00e2m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4045","checkdouble":"190671"},{"date":"10:15 08/07","title":"Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u0103n sao tr\u1ebb h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. H\u1ecd quy\u1ebft s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Aston Villa bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Grealish</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18, Aston Villa gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 play-off, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Middlesbrough \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Fulham song sau c\u00f9ng thua 0-1. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Premier League khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Birmingham \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Tony Xia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Aston Villa s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n \u0111i c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1edbi tai nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i Premier League, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Jack Grealish.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho sao tr\u1ebb 22 tu\u1ed5i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, Aston Villa ra gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Grealish. Nh\u01b0ng sau khi l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua c\u00f9ng Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2017/18, Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0 Tottenham hay Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Grealish. Ph\u00eda Aston Villa hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n ch\u1edd nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish\" title=\"Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/9/7/hlv-hodgson-giuc-sao-tre-aston-villa-som-chon-dtqg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn \u00e1n binh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Mirror, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng Liverpool b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c. H\u1ecd \u00e2m th\u1ea7m theo s\u00e1t Grealish v\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua kim ti\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi chia tay Philippe Coutinho, hi\u1ec7n Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay th\u1ebf. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 ba Mohamed Salah, Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino, HLV Klopp v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-klopp-muon-liverpool-mua-xherdan-shaqiri-172-190490.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-khong-nen-chieu-mo-forsberg-172-190458.html\">Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu-172-190409.html\">Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-len-tieng-choc-tuc-man-utd-172-190403.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\">Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4044","checkdouble":"190672"},{"date":"10:56 08/07","title":"Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/28/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Mane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-giai-cuu-david-luiz-172-189742.html\" target=\"_blank\">Los\u00a0Blancos quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mane</span> c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Sadio-Mane-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real quan t\u00e2m Mane\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Mane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Liverpool, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Firmino v\u00e0 Salah h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 20 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 8 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, anh c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eafc b\u00e9n. Liverpool ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Real hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Los Blancos nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Liverpool b\u1ecf ra 33 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mane t\u1eeb Southampton, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ra g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed m\u00e0 h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mane t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp noi ve Mane\" title=\"Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Mane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/28/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mane h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u00f4ng tin Real quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf M\u1ef9. Real l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf Liverpool.\"</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Klopp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4043","checkdouble":"190673"}]}